dct_title_s: Republic of Georgia administrative GIS spatial data [FSU-AC3+]
dct_description_sm: Includes ADM1 and ADM2 administrative units and capitals for the Republic of Georgia, current to the early to mid 2000s.  The spatial data are geo-referenced in decimal degrees using the WSG84 Spheriod, and incorporate DCW coastlines and international boundaries.
System requirements: IBM or compatible computer; CD-ROM drive; software capable of reading an ESRI shapefile, such as ArcGIS.
dct_creator_sm: Asian Spatial Information and Analysis Network (Australia), Australian Centre
dct_publisher_sm: Australian Centre of the Asian Spatial Information and Analysis Network
